71b8e53b-4c95-4d67-aacf-0434f833fc47	Purpose LImitiation	Only collect, use or disclose personal data for the purposes that a reasonable person would consider appropriate under the given circumstances and for which the individual has given consent.\n\nAn organisation may not, as a condition of providing a product or service, require the individual to consent to the collection, use or disclosure of his or her personal data beyond what is reasonable to provide that product or service.	\N	2025-07-02 18:32:04.114242+00	2025-08-25 17:00:32.550933+00	published	node_1751487779564	5	\N	lesson	\N
