fcbb989f-565d-4f87-8a65-a419ba7b69e1	Intro to HIB	This lesson provides an overview of the Health Information Bill 	56e2b62a-c393-4bcf-ae6d-1b8c4b0fa823	2025-09-11 05:34:26.438183+00	2025-09-12 00:52:40.062669+00	published	node_1757592037333	10	\N	lesson	\N
